                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 13739/2.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Minister <persName type="to">Fox</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-06-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 20, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Adee directs Mr. Fox to convey to the minister for foreign affairs
                    department’s congratulations on the completion of the railway to Quito.)</p>
            </div>
